  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "A BILL TO AMEND THE SOUTH CAROLINA CODE OF LAWS BY ENACTING THE \"LIFE BEGINS AT CONCEPTION ACT\" BY AMENDING SECTIONS 44-41-630 AND 44-41-650, RELATING TO THE \"FETAL HEARTBEAT AND PROTECTION FROM ABORTION ACT\", SO AS TO PROHIBIT ABORTIONS AFTER CONCEPTION; BY PROVIDING THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY THE RIGHT TO INTERVENE IN LEGAL CHALLENGES TO THE ACT; AND TO RETITLE ARTICLE 6, CHAPTER 41, TITLE 44, AS \"LIFE BEGINS AT CONCEPTION\"."
    }
